    {
      "id": "activity-scheduler",
      "title": "Activity Scheduler",
      "description": "My first side project, built with Laravel and Metronic Admin Panel.",
      "paragraphs": [
        "Around 2020, my coworker asked me if I could build a web application for his friend at clinic, he said his friend just need a simple activity scheduler.\nSince I've never work on a side project before, I said yes and hoping I would be able to learn something new.",
        "So, what this application does is like a task list for activities, if they've done it, then mark as done, otherwise mark as not done and provide a reason why.\nIt was a fun project because if I remember it correctly, at the time I was using Livewire and learned so much about it."
      ],
      "tags": [
        "PHP",
        "Laravel"
